{"tid":38903,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵翻隻太空冒險game","createTime":"2016-12-14T08:36:35.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T15:59:23.000Z","uid":12193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"89cd849746997770b79d806eaeb8b4b4057fbc13","tid":38903,"uid":12193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T08:36:35.000Z","msg":"好年前既PC game (大概08咁上下)<br />\n遊戲內容大概係:<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 行商(係A星平買到B星高賣)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 太空戰鬥<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有分唔同勢力既人  做任務會令你偏去某一勢力 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係太空會偶遇敵對勢力開拖<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係星球附近鳩打人會有太空警察打鳩你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最大印象係太空個到有啲高速公路 一個個環 好似check point咁 入左去可以加速擺脫敵人<br />\n呢隻game好似有漢化<br />\n舊電腦壞左就搵唔翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求求大家幫手"},{"pid":"c16f6beef6257f86e7a4771885dd1158139d656a","tid":38903,"uid":30092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T08:40:06.000Z","msg":"Freelancer"},{"pid":"4287453a8fe7f2439d74d1cb71b41152566e5c02","tid":38903,"uid":12193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:40:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Freelancer</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbef7f5573f67830c18489c2ae47d8491b3e5e78","tid":38903,"uid":56647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T15:59:23.000Z","msg":"巴打 有冇玩EVE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" cl